reviewText: Had minimal value to me. But someone else might love it.

I was frantically searching for a video overview to show my students when i stumbled upon this in Amazon prime. Not exactly what i was looking for but interesting. The students got another view of mask making using different materials than those used in their assignment.

While this could have used a bit of editing, it was very helpful indeed to see the process of working with leather. The artist was encouraging, putting this kind of mask-making accessible even to the inexperienced. It was great that the consecration and some use was included.
